    <div class="pure-u-1-3">
      <p>While registering for NodeJack, you implicitly agree to my terms of service.  That is to say, don't be a jerk, I am just trying to give you a game.  If you find any bugs, notify me at <a href="http://github.com/floodric/NodeJack">my github</a></p>
    </div>
    -->
  </div>  
</body>
</html>
